<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="app-mark">P</view>
    <view class="title">Passbox</view>
    <view class="version">{{version}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">作者</view>
    <view class="row">
      <view class="row-title">619</view>
      <view class="row-text">Passbox 的设计与开发者。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">功能介绍</view>
    <view class="row">
      <view class="row-title">账号密码管理</view>
      <view class="row-text">记录不同平台的账号、密码、备注和自定义图标。</view>
    </view>
    <view class="row">
      <view class="row-title">密码默认隐藏</view>
      <view class="row-text">进入详情页时密码默认折叠，需要主动点击才会显示。</view>
    </view>
    <view class="row">
      <view class="row-title">云端加密同步</view>
      <view class="row-text">账号库加密后同步到微信云开发数据库，不直接上传明文密码。</view>
    </view>
    <view class="row">
      <view class="row-title">批量管理</view>
      <view class="row-text">支持选择多个账号并批量删除，删除后同步云端。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">注意事项</view>
    <view class="row">
      <view class="row-title">请保护设备安全</view>
      <view class="row-text">当前版本以体验和功能验证为主，建议不要在公共设备上保存重要密码。</view>
    </view>
    <view class="row">
      <view class="row-title">云端保存的是密文</view>
      <view class="row-text">数据库中应只看到 encryptedVault 等密文字段，不应出现明文密码。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">GitHub</view>
    <view class="github-card" bindtap="copyGithub">
      <view class="github-text">{{github}}</view>
      <view class="copy-text">复制</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
